Title: 133: How a Passion for Tableau Changed a Life
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the Founder of The Information Lab, Tom Brown. You will hear about the origins of the Data School, discover a Tableau addiction, and be inspired by how passionate Tom is about Tableau and how that passion has driven his career and shaped him along the way.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/133
